WEBVTT

00:05.772 --> 00:08.172
Hey, whatcha doin'?

00:08.241 --> 00:10.209
Just countin'
my secret stash.

00:10.276 --> 00:13.404
- I'm gettin' something special for Donna.
- Something special, huh?

00:13.480 --> 00:15.778
Oh, is it firecrackers?

00:15.849 --> 00:17.407
No.

00:17.484 --> 00:20.647
No, no, 'cause if it's somethin'
that blows up, I'll go halfsies.

00:25.058 --> 00:27.424
It's a promise ring.

00:27.527 --> 00:30.553
'Cause, you know, Donna and I
have been fighting a lot lately.

00:30.630 --> 00:32.598
Forman, you get
mushy with Donna...

00:32.665 --> 00:35.498
she's gonna see
the secret girl inside the man.

00:37.837 --> 00:41.034
Now, trust me, you don't
want to let Erica out.

00:42.475 --> 00:45.171
Erica.

00:45.245 --> 00:47.509
That's a good burn.

00:47.580 --> 00:50.947
You can't do that
with Michael. I'm lucky.

00:51.017 --> 00:53.281
Oh, really, Michelle?

00:55.088 --> 00:57.022
Oh, I forgot
about Michelle.

00:58.525 --> 01:02.017
Look, Hyde obviously doesn't
understand mature relationships...

01:02.095 --> 01:04.063
but I do.

01:04.129 --> 01:06.963
And a promise ring is not only
a gift from the heart...

01:07.033 --> 01:10.127
but it also means more sex
and less mouthing off.

01:11.738 --> 01:13.865
I'm gettin' one for Jackie too!

01:13.940 --> 01:15.703
Great.
Let's go.

01:15.775 --> 01:18.437
All right.
See you later, Hyde-a...

01:18.511 --> 01:20.445
alicia.

01:21.781 --> 01:24.181
What's a good
girlie name for Hyde?

01:24.250 --> 01:27.242
Uh, Hyde...

01:27.320 --> 01:29.550
drangea?

01:29.622 --> 01:31.647
It's Heidi,
you morons! Heidi!

01:35.462 --> 01:38.920
Okay, is it me, or is this not a ring store?

01:41.301 --> 01:44.998
Will you trust me?
I know a guy who knows a guy.

01:45.071 --> 01:47.005
He'll be here any minute.

01:50.910 --> 01:53.105
Hey, dudes.

01:55.115 --> 01:57.345
Leo's the guy?

01:57.417 --> 01:59.612
Kelso, I thought you knew
a guy who knew a guy.

01:59.686 --> 02:01.711
Yeah, I do.

02:03.289 --> 02:05.314
But I know Leo.

02:06.759 --> 02:09.158
Fine, so you're the guy!

02:12.265 --> 02:15.291
So, Leo,
you sell promise rings?

02:15.368 --> 02:18.337
Promise rings,
concert T's...

02:18.404 --> 02:20.338
other stuff.

02:25.145 --> 02:27.136
- Really?
- That's nice.

02:27.213 --> 02:29.147
Yeah.

02:30.884 --> 02:32.818
Okay, we'll take
two rings and...

02:32.886 --> 02:35.150
a misdemeanor's worth
of the other stuff.

